interactions.flavorLineOne: Both Louis and his lifelong friend appreciate the thoughtful gift you've brought them. Louis seems calmer already.

Represent your clan well, Guardian.

This banner will grow in strength as your clan demonstrates its power.
Hawthorne congratulates you and your friend on reaching a significant milestone, and she offers a reward to help celebrate.
Hawthorne doesn't trust the Drifter, but she supports you and your friend working together to push back the enemies of humanity.
Hawthorne congratulates you and your friend on reaching a significant milestone, and she offers a reward to help celebrate.

Your vision from the Traveler was true and it led you back to the Light. The camp is even safer now that you have reconnected to your power. But there are still a lot of people out there in the wild who need refuge. Help get them to the Farm. 

Go meet Hawthorne's friend Devrim by selecting the landing zone TROSTLAND in the EDZ.

Hawthorne prefers the solitary life, choosing to live beyond the Wall. Despite this, she took charge of this camp to help the refugees of the City survive in unfamiliar and dangerous lands. She wants to help you out and offers you a ship for your journey. 

Follow your vision to the Shard of the Traveler by completing mission SPARK in the EDZ.

We have witnessed the miraculous: the Traveler has reawakened… and Hawthorne has returned to the City. Zavala convinced her to continue her role as guide for both new and old Guardians. She found her place in this new community, bridging the gap between humanity and the Guardians who protect them. 

Visit Hawthorne for all of your clan-related activities.
Hawthorne doesn't trust the Drifter, but she supports you and your friend working together to push back the enemies of humanity.

We have a new plan. The Vanguard will lead a host of Lightless Guardians on a counteroffensive against the occupied City, hoping to free the Traveler. Meanwhile, you must disable the Almighty's sun-killing superweapon before it can destroy the entire solar system. To approach the Almighty undetected, steal the personal ship of Thumos the Unbroken, one of Ghaul's chosen Blood Guard. 

Bring the fight back to the Red Legion by completing mission "Payback" in the EDZ.
Hawthorne recognizes your shared commitment with another Guardian and is eager to challenge the two of you to prove that connection.
